The paper deals with brain tumor segmentation using machine learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of deep learning models and interactive segmentation also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of natural language processing (NLP) techniques for text analysis, which falls under the computational linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category.
